      <acqinfo id="aspace_406203bf325e973cab9e0ce98d867921">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The Collection of Twentieth-Century Graphic Art was housed in the former Arts of the Book Collection until its transfer to the Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library in 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_a0c0c96a6ab8f9bd17d2450e00ba61d9">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
