      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_95117ea5c0ecc07e98d378bafb17e1a7">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Collection of Twentieth-Century Graphic Art, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_9d2732ab2b6588410a7d94dc38a90fab">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains examples of graphic art from 1900-1999. Many of these materials are not dated; an educated guess as to the age of the material was based on paper type and subject matter.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_77a9c197c2dc6721197e00dfbffde853">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into five series: I. Posters. II. Prints. III. Maps &amp; Diagrams. IV. Reproductions of Artwork. V. Miscellaneous.</p>  
      </arrangement>
